T02TD1307E:217b-1: nee r'atma de pi panytsa da sha sto tra /
T02TD1307E:217b-3: bdag med ma lha mo bco lnga la bstod pa /
T02TD1307E:217b-4: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:217b-5: mos pa sna tshogs gdul dka' 'dul ba'i phyir //
T02TD1307E:217b-6: chos dbyings mi bskyod 'gag pa med pa las //
T02TD1307E:217b-7: thabs kyis sprul pa sna tshogs ston mdzad pa //
T02TD1307E:217b-8: ye shes thugs rje can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:217b-9: 'khor lo bzhi yi bdag nyid aa las skyes //
T02TD1307E:217b-10: bdud bzhi zil gyis gnon pa 'jigs pa'i sku //
T02TD1307E:217b-11: mi bskyod dbu brgyan bde ba chen po'i ngang //
T02TD1307E:217b-12: ye shes mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:217b-13: a'a las skyes pa'i mdzes ma rdo rje ma //
T02TD1307E:218a-0: rtag tu dgyes pas kha tv'am @218a * //
T02TD1307E:218a-2: gdug pa rnam skrag rnam snang cod pan thogs //
T02TD1307E:218a-3: dur khrod rgyan dang ldan la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218a-4: ai las byung ba'i gsang ba'i goo r'i ma //
T02TD1307E:218a-5: gzi brjid mi mtshungs gar ldan ro mchog myang //
T02TD1307E:218a-6: don dam thugs chud dbu rgyan rin chen tog / spyan gsum thod rlon can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218a-7: a'a li k'a li'i snyoms 'jug rnal 'byor ma //
T02TD1307E:218a-8: bde la rtag dgyes byang chub sems kyi ngang //
T02TD1307E:218a-9: 'od dpag med kyis dbu brgyan a'i las skyes //
T02TD1307E:218a-10: gar gyis dgyes pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218a-11: au las byung ba'i rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1307E:218a-12: khams gsum dag byed sgrol ma las kyi mchog / don grub dbu brgyan chags pa'i spyan dang ldan //
T02TD1307E:218a-13: mtshungs med chags par ldan la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218a-14: skye med chos dbyings rnam dag pukka s'i //
T02TD1307E:218a-15: mi bskyod dbu brgyan dri ma dag mdzad cing //
T02TD1307E:218a-16: au las skyes pa brgya phyed phreng ba 'dzin //
T02TD1307E:218a-17: 'jig rten zhi mdzad de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218a-18: dus gsum 'dus ma byas pa'i ri khrod ma //
T02TD1307E:218a-19: spros bral dri med rnam snang dbu la bzhugs //
T02TD1307E:218a-20: ri las 'khrungs pa gar gyis phyogs bcur gzigs //
T02TD1307E:218a-21: chu zla dang mtshungs khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218a-22: gnas dang nye gnas la sogs bgrod mdzad cing //
T02TD1307E:218a-23: 'du byed ma lus sreg mdzad tsandal'i //
T02TD1307E:218a-24: rin chen dbu brgyan brjid pas r'i las skyes //
T02TD1307E:218a-25: 'dzag pa gsal mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218a-26: mi gnas mya ngan 'das pa'i bdag nyid las //
T02TD1307E:218a-27: thugs rje skyed mdzad g-yo ba'i dombi n'i //
T02TD1307E:218a-28: sgeg mo snang mthas dbu brgyan li las byung //
T02TD1307E:218a-29: mkha' ltar dri med sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218a-30: shin tu grag pa'i brda yi skad sbyor zhing //
T02TD1307E:218a-31: ru dhi ra dang aantra la rtag dgyes //
T02TD1307E:218a-32: zhe sdang rdo rjes dbu brgyan l'i las skyes //
T02TD1307E:218a-33: goo r'i phyogs bcur gzigs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218a-34: chos nyid gsal ba'i yum gyur chom rkun ma //
T02TD1307E:218a-35: mi rtog mnyam nyid 'gro ba'i don la brtson //
T02TD1307E:218a-36: dbu rgyan gti mug rdo rje mi 'gyur rtags //
T02TD1307E:218a-37: ae las bskyed pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218a-38: 'jig rten ma lus chags las dbang du mdzad //
T02TD1307E:218a-39: dpal ldan gzi brjid skyed mdzad be t'a l'i //
T02TD1307E:218a-40: nga rgyal rdo rjes dbu brgyan aee las skyes //
T02TD1307E:218b-0: snyoms 'jug mi gnas @218b ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218b-1: shes rab thabs su ldan pa'i gha sma r'i //
T02TD1307E:218b-2: de nyid las skyes 'dod chags rdo rjes brgyan //
T02TD1307E:218b-3: ao las byung ba drag po las las skyes //
T02TD1307E:218b-4: skye med skye bar bstan la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218b-5: sgyu ma smig rgyu bzhin du mkha' la spyod //
T02TD1307E:218b-6: bar snang mnga' mdzad he ru ka yi ngang //
T02TD1307E:218b-7: cod pan snang ba mtha' yas aoo las skyes //
T02TD1307E:218b-8: thams cad mkhyen cing gzigs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218b-9: rnam snang mdzad kyis dbu brgyan sa 'og spyod //
T02TD1307E:218b-10: 'og gi 'jig rten ma lus sgrol mdzad ma //
T02TD1307E:218b-11: aam las byung ba'i dur khrod 'jigs pas brgyan //
T02TD1307E:218b-12: thabs mkhas thugs rje can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218b-13: a'a li k'a li zla ba nyi ma kha sbyor sa 'og rnam par dag pa las //
T02TD1307E:218b-14: gri gug thod pa la sogs phyag rgya lnga yis brgyan pa mdzes mdzad cing //
T02TD1307E:218b-15: skyil krung phyed pa'i gar ldan gcer bu spyan gsum stag lpags sham thabs can //
T02TD1307E:218b-16: phyag rgya chen po'i sku la rtsa gsum sprul mdzad de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1307E:218b-17: bsod nams ye shes chen po las byung sku lnga ye shes lngar ldan 'jigs pa'i gzugs can ma //
T02TD1307E:218b-18: bdag nyid dad pa'i mthu yis rgyu yi yon tan shas tsam mthong nas dad pa'i dbyangs kyis bstod pa yis //
T02TD1307E:218b-19: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor gnas pa'i rnam rtog rlung gis rgya mtsho phyogs bcur g-yeng ba rnams //
T02TD1307E:218b-20: skye rga na 'chi spangs nas 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las brgal bla med byang chub thob par shog //
T02TD1307E:218b-21: slob dpon mi thub zla bas mdzad pa'o//
